# JanSeva — Indian Government Welfare Schemes Platform

A **free, ad-supported web application** that helps Indian citizens discover, understand, and apply for Central & State government welfare schemes. An AI engine recommends the best-fit schemes based on the user's profile.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **App Name**: I'm proposing **"JanSeva"** (जनसेवा — Service to People). Would you prefer a different name?

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Tech Stack Decision**: For the MVP, I'm proposing a **single-page web app using Vite + vanilla JS** (no heavy framework). This keeps it lightweight, fast, and easy to deploy. If you want a full-stack app with backend/database right away, we'd need to discuss hosting. Please confirm.

> [!WARNING]
> **Scheme Data**: Real government scheme data would need to be sourced from official APIs or manually curated. For the MVP, I'll create a **realistic sample database** of ~20-30 popular schemes (PM-KISAN, Ayushman Bharat, MGNREGA, etc.) with accurate eligibility criteria. You can expand this later.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **AI Feature**: For the AI scheme matcher, I'll implement a **rule-based matching engine** (no API costs) that scores schemes based on user profile fields (age, income, category, state, occupation). A future upgrade could integrate an actual LLM. Does this approach work for you?

