## Core Features (MVP)

| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| 🏠 **Landing Page** | Hero section, feature highlights, testimonials, CTA |
| 👤 **User Profile** | Age, gender, income, state, category (SC/ST/OBC/General), occupation, family size |
| 📋 **Scheme Browser** | Browse all schemes with filters (Central/State, category, sector) |
| 🔍 **Search** | Full-text search across scheme names and descriptions |
| 🤖 **AI Matcher** | Rule-based engine that recommends top schemes for the user's profile |
| 📄 **Scheme Detail** | Eligibility, benefits, required documents, how to apply (online + offline) |
| 📝 **Apply Help** | Direct links to official portals + downloadable document checklists |
| 📢 **Ad Integration** | Google AdSense banner & interstitial ad placeholders |
| 🌐 **Multi-language** | English + Hindi toggle (MVP) |

